description:
Agency provides emergency food, clothing and networks with other agencies to help resolve problems.

Help is given on emergency basis, ONCE EVERY YEAR. If client has received help from them before, they must be in an extreme emergency situation to receive help again; if they receive help a second time, they will only receive a Care Package (bread and pastries).

Thanksgiving 2016:
If available will be providing turkeys to take home.
name: PASS IT ON MINISTRIES - EMERGENCY FOOD PROGRAM
